No. 664. Clinton Stephens, Jr., Petitioner, v. Essex County Park Commission. April 16, 1906. Mr. Andrew Wilson and Mr. Noel W. Barksdale for petitioner. Mr. Robert H. McCarter and Mr. Alonzo Church for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the-Third Circuit denied.
